<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.4">
<l>cāntēn tumeṉmulaiyār taṭantōḷpuṇa riṉpaveḷḷat</l>
<l>tāḻntē ṉarunakarat taḻuntumpa yaṉpaṭaittēṉ</l>
<l>pōntēṉ puṇṇiyaṉē yuṉṉaiyeytiyeṉ tīviṉaikaḷ</l>
<l>tīrntēṉ niṉṉaṭaintēṉ tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I drowned in a deluge of the delight of embrace in the wide arms</l>
<l rend="indent">of [women] with soft, high breasts with sandal paste;</l>
<l>I created the consequence of sinking into severe hell.</l>
<l>Pure one, I came reaching for you [instead]; I ended my evil karma.</l>
<l>I take refuge in you, [Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
